Indiana Pacers player Chris Copeland and his wife Katrine Saltare were stabbed outside a club in Chelsea early on Wednesday morning . 
  Shezoy Murdock , 22 , allegedly interrupted them as they argued and pulled out a knife . 
  Copeland told the man to back off and he was stabbed in the abdomen and elbow . 
  Pero Antic and Thabo Sefolosha of the Atlanta Hawks were arrested at the scene for allegedly obstructing police . 
  The couple are in stable condition at Bellevue Hospital . 
 